        <title>索尼手机距离感应器故障导致通话黑屏无法挂电话的解决方法</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/sony-phone-malfunction/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 25 Sep 2017 13:31:47 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/sony-phone-malfunction/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;目前主力手机 SONY Xperia Z5 在一次摔落碎屏后，用联想的碎屏保险进行了换屏维修，手机回来后开始出现通话无法主动挂机，导致某些时候出现一些异常尴尬…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;因为很少用电话联系所以没去理，最近打电话联系顺丰客服因为黑屏无法按数字呼人工服务，无论按音量键、电源键还是相机键都无法唤醒屏幕，实在忍无可忍。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;查到的资料是说光线感应器或者距离感应器坏了，去手机维修店很好搞。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是这台快退役的  Z5 实在不想去修，然后还看到一个方法是“电话”应用里面设置关闭距离传感器，但是索尼固件的原生“电话”应用没有这个设置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最后用一个第三方电话应用 “ &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.coolapk.com/apk/com.candykk.android.dialer&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Candy 电话&lt;/a&gt; ” 解决，界面类似原生的，在“高级设置”项里可以禁用距离传感器，EZ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;778&#34; height=&#34;557&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4892&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone.png 778w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone-150x107.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone-300x215.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/candy-phone-768x550.png 768w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>SONY Xperia Z3C 更换后盖</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/sony-z3c-cover/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 18 Feb 2016 16:59:45 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/sony-z3c-cover/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;大概半年前，我的 Z3C 摔了几次，然后后盖就碎成这样了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1094&#34; height=&#34;730&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-3892&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW.jpg 1094w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW-150x100.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW-300x200.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Z3C-WW-1024x683.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1094px) 100vw, 1094px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本来还碎的挺好看的，不过后来一些玻璃渣开始掉落，加上裂缝中进了很多灰尘，实在没办法，只能换后盖了，然后发现淘宝竟然有十几块包邮的Z3C后盖，毫不犹豫拍下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;直接暴力手段卸开后来，iPad 拍摄渣画质。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-1.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;778&#34; height=&#34;581&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-z3c-cover-1&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4782&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-1.jpg 778w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-1-150x112.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-1-300x224.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;778&#34; height=&#34;581&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-z3c-cover-2&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4783&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-2.jpg 778w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-2-150x112.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-2-300x224.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;和原厂后盖有点色差，不过整体看起来还不错。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-3.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;778&#34; height=&#34;581&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-z3c-cover-3&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-4784&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-3.jpg 778w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-3-150x112.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/sony-z3c-cover-3-300x224.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 778px) 100vw, 778px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>SONY Xperia Z3C 升级 Android 5.1.1 保留 ROOT &amp; REC</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/sony-xperia-z3c-android-5-1-1-root-rec/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2015 18:29:58 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/sony-xperia-z3c-android-5-1-1-root-rec/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;最近 Z3C 收到了 Android 5.1.1 的 OTA ，因为手机已 ROOT ，无法验证，只能通过卡刷的方式更新，这样才可以保留 ROOT 和 REC 。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #99cc00;&#34;&gt;5.1.1 是个很重要的版本，该版本修复了 Lollipop 固件中的内存泄漏 Bug ，在 Android M 还没着落的时候还是先刷上 5.1 先吧。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;索尼的手机折腾起来真的挺麻烦的，ROOT 和 REC 什么的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不打算写详细的教程，汇总下需要的教程再整理下过程。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ff0000;&#34;&gt;&lt;/em&gt; 在升级之前请备份手机的重要数据&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4.4.4 和 5.0.2 固件的先 ROOT 和刷入 REC ，如果当前固件没有合适的 ROOT 工具，先用 FlashTool 强刷到合适的版本。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4.4  ROOT ：&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://bbs.gfan.com/android-7829711-1-1.html&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;XDA|Z3/Z3C免解锁ROOT|一键ROOT与REC工具|giefroot_v3定制版&lt;/a&gt;{#thread_subject}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5.0 ROOT ：&lt;a href=&#34;http://bonnieee.co/2464/root-xperia-lollipop&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;懶人式一鍵ROOT工具 – Xperia Lollipop 5.0專用&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FlashTool 下载：&lt;a href=&#34;http://bbs.gfan.com/android-8036255-1-1.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;索尼Xperia手机刷机工具 &lt;span class=&#34;cred&#34;&gt;FlashTool&lt;/span&gt; 0.9.19.0 汉化优化版&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;强刷教程：&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.anqu.com/study_621/51327/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;索尼Xperia系列Flashtool强刷图文教程&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;强刷驱动问题：&lt;a href=&#34;http://tieba.baidu.com/p/2227615547&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;解决windows8下不能安装flashtool+fastboot驱动问题&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;下载带 ROOT 和 REC 的 5.1.1 固件卡刷包，进入 REC 三清 Wipe 再刷入，然后关机。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://bbs.gfan.com/android-8026444-1-1.html&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;索尼5.1 Z3C 带最新root和rec卡刷包&lt;/a&gt;{#thread_subject}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;下载 5.1.1 的官方固件然后强刷 5.1.1 的官方固件内核。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p id=&#34;_disk_id_23&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a href=&#34;http://pan.baidu.com/s/1hUb0q&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Z3C 5.1.1 官方固件（D5803 23.4.A.0.546 Customized BAL）&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://bbs.gfan.com/android-8027318-1-1.html&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;z3c刷完5.1.1无限重启的的进，你们需要关机强刷下对应的内核&lt;/a&gt;{#thread_subject}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;官方版的 Xposed 框架暂时还不支持 Android 5.1 ，可以刷其他大牛制作的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下载下面链接里面的 &lt;a href=&#34;http://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?s=65a46e13099e0be34f24bc4db90e1efe&amp;attachmentid=3420636&amp;d=1438030312&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;posed-v68-sdk22-arm-by-romracer&lt;/a&gt; 在 REC 刷入，再安装 Xposed Installer（3.0 alpha4 ），64位手机下载 arm64 的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;a-hrefhttpforumxda-developerscomxposedsuper-alpha-posted-permission-xposed-t3072979-target_blankxposed-for-android-51-8211-v68--20150727--sdk22a&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#a-hrefhttpforumxda-developerscomxposedsuper-alpha-posted-permission-xposed-t3072979-target_blankxposed-for-android-51-8211-v68--20150727--sdk22a&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;http://forum.xda-developers.com/xposed/super-alpha-posted-permission-xposed-t3072979&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Xposed for Android 5.1 – v68 / 20150727 / SDK22&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;经过以上多番折腾，手机终于可以愉快的使用了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5.1.1 固件相比之前 5.0.2 流畅了不少，还有个小变化，下拉菜单可以直接连接 WIFI 或者蓝牙而不用跳转设置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/sony-xperia-5.1.1.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-4444&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/sony-xperia-5.1.1.png&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-5.1.1&#34; width=&#34;450&#34; height=&#34;720&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/sony-xperia-5.1.1.png 450w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/sony-xperia-5.1.1-94x150.png 94w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/sony-xperia-5.1.1-188x300.png 188w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>日版 SONY Xperia Z3 Compact（NTT docomo SO-02G）</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/sony-xperia-z3c/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2015 10:59:28 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/sony-xperia-z3c/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;昨天不愉快的事还没结束，退款还得等，手头只剩2K多，只能买Z3C了，果断上了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第二位卖家准时发货，今天准时收到。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;盒子超小，一个巴掌大。&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3553&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-1&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本体，绿色的边框太骚了！&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3554&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-2&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;日版Z3C的后面印着运营商docomo的LOGO而不是索尼的，信仰分-1。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3555&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-3&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;低端卡片相机（DSC-W730）在弱光环境不开闪光灯图片没法看，开了又拍不好。&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3556&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-4&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-4-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;标配没有数据线和电源适配器，只有一个TV信号接收转换头和磁吸式座充及扣具。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3557&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-5&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-5-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用FlashTool强刷了港版的Z3C固件（D5833_23.0.A.2.93_HK），第一次刷的时候失败了，以为变砖了，再来一遍就好了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3558&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;sony-xperia-z3c-6&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1255&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6-150x112.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6-300x224.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sony-xperia-z3c-6-1024x765.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;刷了旧的港版固件后，使用 giefroot_v3 进行ROOT和刷入REC，傻瓜式的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-7.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3559&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-7.png&#34; alt=&#34;xperia-z3c-7&#34; width=&#34;877&#34; height=&#34;523&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-7.png 877w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-7-150x89.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-7-300x179.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 877px) 100vw, 877px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;来，拍张照，死宅不拍风景。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3561&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;xperia-z3c-9&#34; width=&#34;1440&#34; height=&#34;1920&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9.jpg 1440w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9-113x150.jpg 113w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9-225x300.jpg 225w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/xperia-z3c-9-768x1024.jpg 768w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
