        <item>
        <title>记一次不愉快的购物经历</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/unhappy-shopping/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2015 11:54:17 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/unhappy-shopping/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;前几天想着买台相机拍拍照，洗个澡的功夫Nexus 4就碎屏，触控完全失灵那种，只能再买一台手机了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近日版的索尼手机价格大跌，心水已久的Xperia Z3日版只要2K8，比港版便宜了近700，而且储存空间大了16GB，可以通刷港版的ROM，缺点是NFC和省电模式不能用了。长久以来软件更新一直是日系机的最大诟病，通刷港版ROM（国际版）意味着ROOT和系统更新不再是问题，而且NFC暂时还是个鸡肋功能，Z3续航不错，少个省电模式也没什么，入手日版手机最佳时机到了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Z3和Z3 Compact之间纠结了很久，Z3的5.2寸屏幕略大了，而且绿色叫“银绿色”，很淡的绿色，个人不怎么喜欢…不够骚！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Z3 Compact的绿色很赞，但是边框是塑料材质的，而且屏幕只有4.6寸，比Nexus 4还小，但比Z3便宜了600，两难的抉择。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最终因为屏幕够大的原因选择了Z3，在淘宝上一家叫 “熊家通讯馆” 的网店以2888 – 60的价格购入一台银绿色的Z3。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;因为Nexus 4完全不能用，没手机用对我来说就是煎熬，所以在早上就拍下付款，然后和卖家约定当天必发顺丰。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;结果物流信息刷了很久都没有，卖家说他们是晚上11点半才集中发货的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3534&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-1&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第二天醒来发现没送到，物流信息显示卖家是早上11点30才发货的。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/%e3%80%8120150309192925.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3533&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/、20150309192925.png&#34; alt=&#34;、20150309192925&#34; width=&#34;592&#34; height=&#34;338&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/、20150309192925.png 592w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/、20150309192925-150x86.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/、20150309192925-300x171.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 592px) 100vw, 592px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;愤怒的去找卖家说，卖家死活不认，说是通宵发货了但是顺丰早上才拉走。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3535&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-2&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;然后我咨询了下顺丰的客服，顺丰说是不会把凌晨收件录成早上才收件的，那肯定是卖家的没有按时发货了。&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3536&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3.png&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-3&#34; width=&#34;2048&#34; height=&#34;1536&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3.png 2048w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3-150x113.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3-300x225.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-3-1024x768.png 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;客服回复态度恶劣，我一怒之下说要退款，但是客服说要调件回来才退，这样我的手机又拿不到钱又冻结了，我才不干，所以骂了句，然后客服不回复了，我也没申请退款，想着迟一天就算了，艹。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第二天醒来还是没有快递电话，咨询顺丰才知道快件被寄方调回了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3537&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-4&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-4-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;联系客服，客服说按照我的意思申请退款退货，麻痹我才没有申请退款。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是手机没拿到，钱又被冻结了，我有急需手机用，联系客服又不理，被逼只能去申请退款，毕竟这样才是最快能拿回钱的办法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;就这样活生生的被算计了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3538&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-5&#34; width=&#34;1680&#34; height=&#34;1260&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5.jpg 1680w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5-150x113.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-5-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;熊家通讯馆吔屎啦&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e7%86%8a%e5%ae%b6%e9%80%9a%e8%ae%af%e9%a6%86%e5%90%94%e5%b1%8e%e5%95%a6&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;strong&gt;熊家通讯馆，吔屎啦！&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;还好还剩点钱，不够买Z3，但是够买Z3 Compact，天意，上吧，找家客服态度好的就上了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-6.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3539&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-6.png&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-6&#34; width=&#34;925&#34; height=&#34;183&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-6.png 925w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-6-150x30.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-6-300x59.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 925px) 100vw, 925px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;——————-半夜更新————————————&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第二家准时发货，夜晚11点半，熊家通讯馆拒绝了我的退款，™逼我退款又不给我退，申请淘宝介入继续战。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-7.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3544&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-7.png&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-7&#34; width=&#34;605&#34; height=&#34;306&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-7.png 605w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-7-150x76.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-7-300x152.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 605px) 100vw, 605px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;新买的Z3C到了，卖家要求我删帖，并对我实行电话短信轰炸。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-8.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3548&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-8.png&#34; alt=&#34;caonima-8&#34; width=&#34;884&#34; height=&#34;764&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-8.png 884w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-8-150x130.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/caonima-8-300x259.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;————————- 3/13 ————————–&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;拖到最后自动退款了，投诉卖家，最后卖家赔50块了结此事。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>几个手机参数对比网站</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/futuremark-dxomark-gsmarena/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 30 Sep 2014 16:54:42 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/futuremark-dxomark-gsmarena/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;平时收集的几个对选购移动设备可能比较有帮助的网站，以数字评分来量化手机参数，如果发现新的还会更新。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;cpugpu性能a-hrefhttpcnfuturemarkcomhardwaremobile-target_blankfuturemark-hardware-mobilea&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#cpugpu%e6%80%a7%e8%83%bda-hrefhttpcnfuturemarkcomhardwaremobile-target_blankfuturemark-hardware-mobilea&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    CPU&amp;amp;GPU性能：&lt;a href=&#34;http://cn.futuremark.com/hardware/mobile&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Futuremark Hardware Mobile&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;关于Futuremark，Windows上著名的跑分软件PC Mark和3D Mark都是这家出品，现在Futuremark开始推出移动端的跑分软件，而且公布了跑分排行榜。作为测试CPU和GPU性能的老牌软件，应该比安兔兔之流可信很多。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3040&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile.png&#34; alt=&#34;Futuremark Hardware Mobile&#34; width=&#34;1165&#34; height=&#34;960&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile.png 1165w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile-150x123.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile-300x247.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Futuremark-Hardware-Mobile-1024x843.png 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1165px) 100vw, 1165px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;相机性能a-hrefhttpwwwdxomarkcommobiles-target_blankdxomark-mobilea&#34;&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%e7%9b%b8%e6%9c%ba%e6%80%a7%e8%83%bda-hrefhttpwwwdxomarkcommobiles-target_blankdxomark-mobilea&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    相机性能：&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dxomark.com/Mobiles&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;DxOMark Mobile&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DxOMark是一家专业的相机测试机构，对相机传感器的测试一直都被认为是&lt;a class=&#34; wrap external&#34; href=&#34;http://tech.hexun.com/it/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow noreferrer&#34;&gt;业界&lt;i class=&#34;icon-external&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;标杆，已经成为全世界范围内相机杂志及媒体用于测评相机的标准系统，同时在DSC厂商、相机芯片厂商、手机厂商等业界享有盛誉。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #999999;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: small;&#34;&gt;– 和讯 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: small;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
  英语不好没关系，进入&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dxomark.com/Mobiles&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;DxOMark Mobile&lt;/a&gt;的右侧就有个手机相机的排行榜，还显示评分，非常直观。（&lt;del&gt;妈蛋SONY的2000W像素G镜头竟然干不过Apple的祖传800W&lt;/del&gt;！）
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
  详细评测页面有颜色、自动对焦、曝光度等各项的评分，还有样张（少量），最后附上正反总结评价（英文不好不用看了）。
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
